## Manual Trace — `[100, 4, 200, 1, 3, 2]`

```
num_set = {1, 2, 3, 4, 100, 200}
```

| num | num - 1 in set? | Action | Streak |
|---|---|---|---|
| 100 | 99 → No | Start counting → 100 only | 1 |
| 4 | 3 → Yes | Skip | — |
| 200 | 199 → No | Start counting → 200 only | 1 |
| 1 | 0 → No | Start counting → 1, 2, 3, 4 | **4** |
| 3 | 2 → Yes | Skip | — |
| 2 | 1 → Yes | Skip | — |

**Result: `4`** ✅ (`[1, 2, 3, 4]`)

